<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-3510] OffsetIndex thread safety</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3510</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We expose non-volatile variables without a lock and outside the class. We also use an `AtomicInteger` unnecessarily since it&apos;s always modified within a lock.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
